- 
[Compiler options and how to pass them](gradle-compiler-options.html).

- 
[Incremental compilation, caches support, build reports, and the Kotlin daemon](gradle-compilation-and-caches.html).

- 
[Gradle basics and specifics](https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/userguide.html).

- 
[Support for Gradle plugin variants](gradle-plugin-variants.html).

